}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 "WORSHIP NOTES" - }{\plain \fs24 \f8 With the start of the Fall Season, "Modern" (contemporary) Worship will once again \softline
occasionally be a part of our 11:00 AM worship service schedule. During the Fall months, Modern Worship will \softline
occur on September 23, October 7 & 21, and November 4 & 18.  Also, starting on September 30, we will introduce \softline
Setting Four of the Liturgy from Lutheran Service Book (LSB page 208 ff).  We'll use Setting Four during the months \softline
of October and November prior to returning to Setting One for Advent beginning December 2.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Men's Prayer Breakfast:}{\plain \fs24 \f8  Men of the congregation are invited to join other Living Savior men for breakfast, prayer \softline
and Bible study every 2nd and 4th Saturday from 7 - 8:30am. We are currently studying the Book of James. \softline
Questions?  Contact Paul Gross.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
