{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 NEW ADULT BIBLE STUDY!  Who is the Holy Spirit?  What role does He play in salvation and in our Christian life?  \softline
How do we know He is a person, and not just a power or a force?  How does He fit into the Trinity?   }{\plain \fs24 \f8 We will \softline
discuss these and many other questions as we reconvene our Adult Sunday School on September 16, at 9:50 AM 
in Klein Hall.  We will have a collaborative, discussion-oriented, six-week session on the Doctrine of the Holy Spirit, \softline
facilitated by Jason Tolbert.  Don't worry if you miss a session!  You can easily join in any time.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 WOMEN'S BIBLE STUDY OPPORTUNITY!  }{\plain \fs24 \f8 Ladies of Living Savior - I would like to invite you to participate in a \softline
weekly Women's Bible Study on Sunday mornings beginning Sunday, September 9, 2018.  We will be using Cynthia \softline
Heald's {\u8220\'93}Becoming a Woman of Excellence{\u8221\'94} as our first study. It will take approximately 12 weeks to complete.  \softline
Location to be determined! Please contact Jenny Minor if you have any questions.  I hope to see you there!  (The \softline
book can be purchased on Amazon for $7.99)\par
}\pard \fs24\qj\tx-540\tx0\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\tx8910\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800\tx11520\tx12240\tx12960\tx13680\tx14400\tx15120\tx15840\tx16560\tx17280\tx18000\tx18720 
