}{\plain \fs24 \f8 Living Savior will host our}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8  Annual Holiday Bazaar }{\plain \fs24 \f8 on Saturday, Nov. 17, 2018 from 10 am - 5 pm.  Tables available \softline
for church members wanting to participate at no cost.  Non-church members can reserve a table for $25.  Baked \softline
goods and items for a Silent Auction needed.  Proceeds to benefit our Women's Ministry and local hyperthermia \softline
