information.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 CHANCEL CHOIR - }{\plain \fs24 \f8 The Chancel Choir is open to adults (HS age and older) who have a love for singing.  This group \softline
helps support and lead various 8:30 & 11:00 worship services from September through June.  Rehearsals are held \softline
on Wednesday nights from 7:30 until 8:45. Contact Meghan Benson mabenson2@gmail.com}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
